Class WeightedUndirectedGraph<T>

java.lang.Object
UndirectedGraph<T>
WeightedUndirectedGraph<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of vertices in the graph
public class WeightedUndirectedGraph<T>
extends UndirectedGraph<T>
A weighted undirected graph is an undirected graph where a weight can be assigned to all edges of the graph
